object.script:
function getAngle(tx, tz, px, pz) local dx = px - tx local dz = pz - tz local theta = math.deg(math.atan(-dz, -dx)) + 90 return theta end
function getDist(px, pz, tx, tz) return math.sqrt((tx-px)^2+(tz-pz)^2) end
function canMove(d, sf) if d > sf then return true else return false end end
function ws(amount) output.setNumber(1, amount) end
function ad(amount) output.setNumber(2, amount) end
function onTick() local is_driver = input.getBool(1)
local pos_x = input.getNumber(1) local pos_z = input.getNumber(2)
local dest_x = input.getNumber(3) local dest_z = input.getNumber(4)
local pos_angle = input.getNumber(5) * 360
-- angle to get to destination local dest_angle = getAngle(pos_x, pos_z, dest_x, dest_z)
local drive_style = property.getNumber("steering_type")
-- the distance sensors local ds_front = input.getNumber(6) local ds_front_left = input.getNumber(7) local ds_front_right = input.getNumber(8) local ds_rear = input.getNumber(9) local ds_rear_left = input.getNumber(10) local ds_rear_right = input.getNumber(11)
-- distance sensor safe distances local ds_safe_front = property.getNumber("front_dist_tolerance") local ds_safe_front_down = property.getNumber("front_down_dist_tolerance") local ds_safe_rear = property.getNumber("rear_dist_tolerance") local ds_safe_rear_down = property.getNumber("rear_down_dist_tolerance")
-- real distances local rds_front = ds_front - ds_safe_front local rds_front_left = ds_front_left - ds_safe_front_down local rds_front_right = ds_front_right - ds_safe_front_down local rds_rear = ds_rear - ds_safe_rear local rds_rear_left = ds_rear_left - ds_safe_rear_down local rds_rear_right = ds_rear_right - ds_safe_rear_down
local ds_safe_wall = property.getNumber("wall_safe_dist") local ds_safe_down = property.getNumber("ground_safe_dist")
local tank_ts = property.getNumber("tank_turn_speed")
if dest_x ~= 0 and pos_x ~= dest_x and pos_z ~= dest_z or dest_z ~= 0 and pos_x ~= dest_x and pos_z ~= dest_z then dist = getDist(pos_x, pos_z, dest_x, dest_z) if dist > 1 and is_driver then output.setBool(1, true)
local angleDiff = math.floor(dest_angle - pos_angle)
while angleDiff > 360 do angleDiff = angleDiff - 360 end
output.setNumber(5, dest_angle)
output.setNumber(6, pos_angle)
output.setNumber(3, angleDiff)
local dist_multi = 1 if dist < 50 then dist_multi = dist/25 end
local angle_multi = 1 if math.abs(angleDiff) < 50 then angle_multi = math.abs(angleDiff)/25 end
output.setNumber(4, angle_multi)
if angleDiff < 2 and angleDiff > -2 then if canMove(rds_front, ds_safe_wall) then ws(1*dist_multi) ad(0) end elseif angleDiff < 182 and angleDiff > 178 then if canMove(rds_front, ds_safe_wall) then ws(-1*dist_multi) ad(0) end elseif angleDiff > 0 and 180 > angleDiff then if drive_style == 0 then elseif drive_style == 1 then if canMove(ds_safe_down, rds_front_left) and canMove(ds_safe_down, rds_rear_right) then -- if it can turn left ad(-tank_ts*angle_multi) if angle_multi == 1 then ws(0) else ws((0.08/angle_multi)) end end end else if drive_style == 0 then elseif drive_style == 1 then if canMove(ds_safe_down, rds_front_right) and canMove(ds_safe_down, rds_rear_left) then -- if it can turn left ad(tank_ts*angle_multi) if angle_multi == 1 then ws(0) else ws((0.08/angle_multi)) end end end end else output.setBool(1, false) end end end
